OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 07 JUN
OL,4,CEVENTS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2002FThe BBC confirms that Michael
OL,7,FBuerk will leave the Ten o'Clock News
OL,8,Fby the end of the year. Michael Buerk
OL,9,Fconfirmed his plans the previous
OL,10,Fevening, saying:
OL,11,
OL,12,F"By November I will have presented the
OL,13,Fmain evening news more than 4,000
OL,14,Ftimes. It's more than enough."
OL,15,
OL,16,FThe official BBC statement said that he
OL,17,Fwould continue to work as a presenter
OL,18,Fon BBC Radio 4 and on news/current
OL,19,Faffairs specials.
OL,20,
OL,21,FIt also mentioned possible foreign
OL,22,Fassignments, including "babysitting"
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBOn This DayCClean FeedFNat TV
